title: Shia LaBeouf charged with public intoxication in Texas
text: Updated: 10/09 9:03 pm Shia Labeouf (Courtesy: Lucas Films) AUSTIN, Texas (AP) -- Actor Shia LaBeouf has been arrested and charged with public intoxication after an incident in Austin, Texas. Jail records show LaBeouf was booked Friday night into the Travis County Jail and released on his own recognizance. No attorney was listed on the record. He was arrested in the city's Sixth Street entertainment district. The Austin City Limits music festival is taking place there through Sunday.
